    <element name="Draconic Soul" type="Class Feature" source="Tanares RPG 5e" id="ID_TRPG_CLASS_FEATURE_DRAGONBLADE_DRACONIC_SOUL">
        <description>
            <p>At 2nd level, you may choose an archetype that represents
your combat training style: the Fury of the Red Dragon, the
Integrity of the White Dragon, or the Celerity of the Blue
Dragon. Each bestows upon you unique Draconic Powers
and features at the 6th, 10th, 14th, and 18th levels. When a
power refers to elements associated with your Draconic Soul,
use fire for the red dragon, cold for the white dragon, and
lightning for the blue dragon, according to your chosen type.</p>
        </description>
        <sheet display="false">
            <description></description>
        </sheet>
        <rules>
